Following https://github.com/giantswarm/kube-stresscheck

kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/giantswarm/kube-stresscheck/master/examples/node.yaml
Scale the deployoment to 30 copies
kubectl scale --replicas=30 deployment/resource-consumerkubectl

For better auto-scalign instructions, follow https://kubernetes.io/blog/2016/07/autoscaling-in-kubernetes/
